<%= link_to 'New Report', new_report_path, :class => 'btn btn-primary pull-right' %>
<h1>CMU WiFi Outage Reporter</h1>

<p>The CMU Networking group claims that no students report WiFi outages. As you know, there was a major outage on 12/2/12. Click "New Report" and fill out the form - we will send them an email for you.</p>

<table class="table table-bordered">
  <tr>
    <th>Name</th>
    <th>Location</th>
    <th>Story</th>
  </tr>

<% @reports.each do |report| %>
  <tr>
    <td><%= link_to report.name, report %></td>
    <td><%= report.location %></td>
    <td><%= truncate(report.personal, length: 200) %></td>
  </tr>
<% end %>
</table>
